headline: SEI Investments (SEIC) Q2 Earnings Surpass Estimates
summary: SEI (SEIC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +50.85% and -0.26%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Seven Ameriprise Financial Advisors Named to Barron’s "Top 100 Women Financial Advisors" List
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, July 23, 2025--Ameriprise Financial announced that seven of the firm’s financial advisors were named to Barron’s list of the "Top 100 Women Financial Advisors."
